result.name: Kam Ka Lok Restaurant

reviews.text: Very average food and dirty place

This is a very down to earth,  reliable and authentic Cha Chaan Teng in the neighbourhood of Tai Kok Tsui.

Nothing gimmicky nothing touristy it is seriously one of the best Cha Chaan Teng I have ever been to in Hong Kong,  and I have been to quite many.

Taste good and authentic Hong Kong. 
Reasonable price,  good portion. 
Friendly (Cha Chaan Teng style) staff.
Free sweet soup at dinner time.

Can be very busy during early dinner time. 
Street parking available.
Cash only.
Local hk style cafe serving almost all day long. The dinner dishes are of good quality.
Great food, there is an english menu. The portion is also quite large.
One of the best Chinese restaurant in tai kok tsui, highly recommend for everyone , must try . 👍
